## Architecture Summary

```
Player clicks "Intervene" in UI
    ↓
POST /api/rpg/adventure/simulation/action
    ↓
apply_player_action_endpoint()
    ↓
apply_player_action(sim_state, action)
    ├─ Idempotency check (action_id)
    ├─ Append consequence (not mutation)
    ├─ Append event
    └─ Record action_diff
    ↓
step_simulation_state()
    ├─ Builds effects from consequences
    ├─ Effects apply to pressure/heat
    └─ Generates incidents/scenes
    ↓
Return {updated_setup, simulation_state, scenes, ...}